Enemy Bomber AttackEarth06/07/3038This is an emergency situation. Longrange radar has detected an enemybomber fleet. You are the only attackcraft in the area.3 long range enemy bombers are high upin the atmosphere - and approachingFedNet civillian targets. Scans reporteach hold 7 tactical fighters armedwith high energy laser canons and A-T-Amissiles.Leave your transport craft andeliminate the bombers before theyreach their targets.Avoid dogfighting - you are outnumbered.When complete, return to the Mothershipand wait for support.#